306861.このたび『マイハウス・マイガーデン』の\n機能が 入りました！\n機能の説明です:
We are pleased to announce the introduction of a brand new feature: My House and My Garden! Here is a run down.
You can register currently placed furniture as a set, and you can rearrange any furniture registered in this way.
In the case of a My House, the house kit used must match.
For a My Garden, the house kit, residential area type, and plot size must all match.
When repositioning registered furniture, you can choose to place them as is or combine them with any current placed furniture.
When placing as is, any currently placed furniture will go to Furniture Storage, and any replicas will be removed.
In the case of combining both, your currently place furniture will remain as is, with the registered furniture placed alongside it.
When rearranging, any furniture that is not in Furniture Storage will not be placed. Replica furniture will still be placed.
Furniture with placement restrictions cannot be registered in a My House or My Garden.
